# Playwright Automation

- Prefer `getByRole`, `getByText`, `locator` with aria-labels over brittle CSS
- Reuse `HumanBehavior` for clicks, typing, scrolling — do not duplicate delay logic
- Screenshot on error to `data/logs/` (pattern: `{context}_error_{username}.png`)
- Respect `pauseState` — call `humanBehavior.checkForPause()` in long flows
- Use `developerMode` shorter delays for local debugging only
- Scope locators to `div[role="dialog"]` when interacting with post modals
- Filter pinned posts: `hasNot: page.locator('svg[aria-label="Pinned post icon"]')`

```typescript
// BAD — global selector, no dialog scope
await page.locator('textarea').fill(comment);

// GOOD — scoped to comment dialog
const dialog = 'div[role="dialog"]';
await page.locator(dialog).locator('textarea[aria-label*="Add a comment"]').fill(comment);
```
